{"tid":1758662,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"失敗由謊言隱瞞開始 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2019-11-27T07:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T14:45:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35d508745ed736b10185c57a841994cb42204b1b","tid":1758662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20191127/20814016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191127%2F20814016%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mREyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=18a39811\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191127%2F20814016%2F&h=54a3f5cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20191127/20814016/</a><br />\n<br />\n失敗由謊言隱瞞開始 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191127/large/1574758460_3372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191127%2Flarge%2F1574758460_3372.jpg&h=ee584819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n區選建制議席輸到開巷，新民黨滅黨，何妖已完，在全城開香檳之際，建制喉舌卻如平行時空，「非戰之罪」、「勝之不武」、「泛民陰招盡出」、「黑色恐怖籠罩」，諉過卸責，死雞硬撐。<br />\n<br />\n嘲笑過後，要問的是，何以有這種和香港主流民情完全不同的誤判？<br />\n<br />\n建制將會大敗，就連建制派自己都估計到，所以大家才會擔心政府會否出陰招取消區議會？而葉國謙也曾帶動風向，明白表示要為區選能否進行定下死線，可見建制派一度真心希望，不要選了，反正輸硬。<br />\n<br />\n但問題是，選舉後來如期，建制派甚至登報紙提出「用選票向暴力說不」，即是說，建制陣營忽然覺得形勢對自己有利，市民不再支持暴力，民意會轉投建制。真的不知那個天才如此研判局勢，這直接導致區選如常進行，建制對泛民，民意卻沒有逆轉，反而一如所料，狠狠懲罰保皇黨。<br />\n<br />\n為何建制派會誤判形勢？因為他們大話講多了，他們天天講「止暴制亂」是全港市民的心願，於是他們認為市民不會怪責警方的暴力，他們認為市民只關心房屋、工作，他們覺得太多的不合作運動會逆轉民意。有一個烽煙節目聽眾講得很好，警察不停打壓取消集會，又用蒙面法嚇怕部份市民不敢聚集上街，於是這幾個月沒有再出現過百萬人的大遊行，而建制派卻認為這就是真實的民意，以為民怨已停民意逆轉以為市民會和手足割席&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n建制派大話講到自己的議席丟了。民意仍然如山聳立，只是有人用大話障目，欺騙自己。<br />\n<br />\n想起清朝的中國人，認為英國人只是炮火厲害，一旦上岸近戰，由於外國人腿僵直不能屈曲，行動不便，清兵很容易便能對付。皇帝心雄，批准交鋒，最後一敗塗地。<br />\n<br />\n為何清廷會以為外國人不能曲腳？因為當初外國使臣朝見皇帝時不肯下跪，為了照顧皇帝面子，清官員唯有欺騙皇上，說外國人的腿腳僵硬不能屈曲。當日的一個謊言，誤判形勢，也就有了後來的一敗塗地。 <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"925b30f2024195c47ad0e11d9bdf4a9c7afaa050","tid":1758662,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad9fa62f07910eabde8276793913b9a93c0522f","tid":1758662,"uid":160991,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"活在同溫層既教訓<br />\n今次建制輸了<br />\n但都要提醒自己唔好犯同樣錯誤"},{"pid":"8bba6d6bd0eef76428e2711cc7b97ed01c530121","tid":1758662,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ad9fa62f07910eabde8276793913b9a93c0522f","tid":1758662,"uid":160991,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"活在同溫層既教訓<br />\n今次建制輸了<br />\n但都要提醒自己唔好犯同樣錯誤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"香港民研<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc70198c1d5e5d91506fdabb573a65e9f9e5b4e9","tid":1758662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad9fa62f07910eabde8276793913b9a93c0522f","tid":1758662,"uid":160991,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"活在同溫層既教訓<br />\n今次建制輸了<br />\n但都要提醒自己唔好犯同樣錯誤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304e23f768b0d4207fbefe59407c3c940248ab6b","tid":1758662,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad9fa62f07910eabde8276793913b9a93c0522f","tid":1758662,"uid":160991,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"活在同溫層既教訓<br />\n今次建制輸了<br />\n但都要提醒自己唔好犯同樣錯誤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"2b17bb003f8176553bf145a70f7baad8f0c35902","tid":1758662,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bba6d6bd0eef76428e2711cc7b97ed01c530121","tid":1758662,"uid":61882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ad9fa62f07910eabde8276793913b9a93c0522f","tid":1758662,"uid":160991,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"活在同溫層既教訓<br />\n今次建制輸了<br />\n但都要提醒自己唔好犯同樣錯誤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"香港民研<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"張建宗話自己無民意調查，要問返出面調查機構，都唔知政府點定政策"}]}